Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄關的門要關好啊  真是不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.12,0:00:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  洗髮水用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵…喵

