Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.21,0:23:04.72,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想以停不住的速度來戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.80,0:23:08.18,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}快點抓住只有兩人的時空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:11.39,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}1 to 3  飛越時空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.52,0:23:14.35,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想與你相會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.39,0:23:18.77,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想如疾風般傳遞給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.94,0:23:22.24,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}再可愛一點地慢慢接近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:27.53,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}化作心形的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.70,0:23:30.41,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}此身只為你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:35.79,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}願伴君左右

